Package: llm-usage-indicator
Version: 0.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-pip, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-3.0
Recommends: gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1, gnome-shell-extension-appindicator, waybar
Maintainer: llm-usage-indicator contributors
Description: LLM usage indicator for Waybar / system tray
 Tracks Claude / Gemini / OpenAI usage and remaining monthly budget.
 Shows live costs in Waybar, the system tray (AppIndicator3 on GNOME,
 Gtk.StatusIcon on X11), or the GNOME top bar.
